Going to SCCOOS station #1.  Orange text = text added by AJD to fill in missing data.  Extrapolated from nearby times. Environmental data transcribed from paper data sheets by AJD for all sightings.
Original lat/lon from visual obs sheets match poorly to GPS tracklines, suspect confusion on lat/lon format.  BJT matching times of visual obs events to GPS trackline from underway data
